Have you tried using #Nitter instead of Twitter frontend?
#Privacy focused #OpenSource alternative for #Twitter?

http://nitter.net
Prevents JS Analytics & 
IP Tracking & 
is lighter

Supports RSS feeds!
- search an account
- click on it 
- the RSS feed is on the top right

